text: Lost time is a concept in traffic engineering. Lost Time may refer to: *Lost Time (12 Rods album), a 2002 album by indie rock band 12 Rods *Lost Time (Tacocat album), a 2016 album by pop punk band Tacocat ==See also== * In Search of Lost Time (French: À la recherche du temps perdu), a novel in seven volumes by Marcel Proust
title: Lost Time
